Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想讓你休息 不過現在不能這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊與目標接觸了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RUDE 你們先繼續待在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人暫時先回總部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標現在的位置...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般士兵 我一個就能解決
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一群纏人的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能打得到我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,72小時之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.63,0:01:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們總務調查部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通稱「TURKS」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接了一個從神羅設施裡逃走的樣本的捕捉任務
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走的樣本是2名成年男子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:01:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一名以前是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「SOLDIER CLASS 1ST」的戰鬥專家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在5年前發生的事件裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和今次事件裡的2人扯上了關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有5年前的那個事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的命運也不會崩潰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個曾經被稱為英雄的最強「SOLDIER」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEPHIROTH
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你為什麼要做這樣的...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就去接你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你在哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的話回答我一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿...是師父...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TIFA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點逃走!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是 SEPHIROTH 做的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEPHIROTH
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEPHIROTH 為什麼要這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你有沒有看見我爸爸?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都找不到他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親的話 應該在魔晄爐的山...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEPHIROTH 也在那山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿! 等等 TIFA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去了也無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TIFA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現目標 發現目標
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前在位置137
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重覆 目前在位置137
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過對付2個人也太小題大作了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在開火範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊我們也要...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用近身戰術擒下他!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是「SOLDIER」的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會棄伙伴而不顧...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「SOLDIER CLASS 1ST」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZACK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:05:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 是你阿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你神智還是清醒的阿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種狀況下怎麼可能還會清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 SEPHIROTH 做的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管他在世間被稱為英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他只不過是一個殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是過份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEPHIROTH 到底想做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你去幫TIFA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tifa 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她為了找她父親 往魔晄爐山去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEPHIROTH 也在那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩不是他的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的對手至少要像是身為「SOLDIER」的你才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是普通的「SOLDIER」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是「SOLDIER CLASS 1ST」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來幫忙大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會盡快追上去幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TIFA 就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「TURKS」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現目標
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問任務是要補捉目標還是直接消滅?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡可能活捉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖投降
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我們就會保證你的生命安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「TURKS」現在才在勸降
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就趁機補捉目標
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個傢伙都跟我開這種玩笑...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要生命安全的保證
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:07:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TIFA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TIFA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃...快點...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 SEPHIROTH 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 SEPHIROTH 做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEPHIROTH
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「SOLDIER」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神羅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔晄爐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全部都最討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來見你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEPHIROTH
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然把我父親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把村裡的人們...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險的時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明約定好會來的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:09:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CLOUD
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標拿到了摩托車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後的逃脫路線將擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZACK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CLOUD
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別生氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能會丟下朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊也真是給了個多餘的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺失目標
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標似乎逃入了地下道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入 MIDGAR... 嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封鎖 MIDGAR 周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TIFA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TIFA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TIFA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TIFA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZACK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被 SEPHIROTH 打傷的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TIFA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了調查才來到這個村莊的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我帶你們參觀了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是這樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變成這樣...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TIFA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神羅「SOLDIER」還有你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭你們大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會求你原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你讓我補償我的罪過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起奪回這個星球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到了一個好方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起到約定的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEPHIROTH
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼殺了村裡的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼打傷了 TIFA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 SEPHIROTH
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親應該用卓越的能力與知識
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為這個星球的支配者才對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他們竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼專長都沒有的他們竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:13:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從母親手中搶走了這個星球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不用再傷心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEPHIROTH
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個背叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEPHIROTH
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我那麼信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經不是我所認識的 SEPHIROTH 了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被選上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被選為這個星球的支配者的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了把這個星球從愚蠢的你們手中奪回給 CETRA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才會誕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了母親
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把母親
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TIFA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有村子都還來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我那麼尊敬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇拜你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TIFA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CLOUD
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遵守了約定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的在我危險的時候來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來晚了點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CLOUD
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會被你這種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CLOUD
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會被你這種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEPHIROTH
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑你們人類就想打倒我嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你知道自己的無能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢...把我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的故鄉給...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀了...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼...可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...到底是...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起到約定的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEPHIROTH
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他們...能夠平安活著就好...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他運到神羅大樓地下室去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEPHIROTH 還真是做了件不得了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝魯特斯主任近來好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣阿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子處理得如何了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始作業了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有必要做到那種地步嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  你還年輕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意見根本怎樣都沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去進行處理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個男人阿...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以當作新的樣本呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有消息聯絡說目標進入警戒範圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上過去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又要...從他們身上搶走自由了嗎...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標已經通過地點48了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  目標使用的摩托車因為燃料耗竭而被丟棄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們為了進入 MIDGAR 而搭了一輛卡車的便車
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主任又擺著一張嚴肅的臉了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5年前明明救了他們  這次是換成要抓他們嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是天意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想他們還真是可憐的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都要同情他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  大家還真是溫柔呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼任務都要完成它  這就是我們的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出擊啦  新人  快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  到了 MIDGAR 你打算怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.71,0:20:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢  總之得先想辦法賺錢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道有什麼生意是我可以做的?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼阿?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該趁年輕試試做每一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趁年輕吃吃各種苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找自己的路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說什麼都可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿  對了  對啦  我有很多其他傢伙沒有知識...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.91,0:20:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  決定了  我要當什麼都做的臨時工
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你  有沒有好好聽我說的話阿?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩的事  危險的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了報酬什麼都做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要變成有錢人囉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  CLOUD
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會丟下你的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:20:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們什麼都做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  知道了嗎?  CLOUD
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標通過地點12
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將近入射程範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要開始囉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們必須等「TURKS」到達之後才能...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有必要把功勞交給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了  快射
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大叔  還沒到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個廢鐵...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CLOUD  快逃
